title: Bellydance-O-Rama Vol 2 DVD Performances by (Nadira, Darshan, Gi
description:
Bellydance-O-Rama Vol 2

I love this series, no odd performances and all of a good standard. Tamra-henna & Aubre together are fantastic, and this also has Sadie for all you Sadie fans.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

See some of the most spectacular belly dance performances in the world on a great stage with state-of-the-art lighting, sound, and video production!

Starring:

Nadira
Darshan
Gina
Roxxanne
Fleurs d'Egypte Dance Company
Virginia
Leyla Jouvana & Roland
Madrina
Habib
Jamileh
Black Opal Dance Company
Isidora Bushkovski
Viviane
Sa'Diyya
Tamra-henna & Aubre
Sadie
LaUra
